OL,3,CUnion members from Aslef to continue
OL,4,Ctrain strikes over the weekend
OL,6,FTrain drivers who are members of the
OL,7,Funion Aslef will strike for 24 hours
OL,8,Fover the weekend.
OL,10,FOn Friday, 5 April, all Avanti West
OL,11,FCoast Services - which run from
OL,12,FHolyhead, Bangor, Llandudno Junction
OL,13,Fand Wrexham to London and Birmingham -
OL,14,Fwill be cancelled.
OL,16,FOn Saturday, 6 April, services will be
OL,17,Flimited.
OL,19,FTransport For Wales services will not
OL,20,Fbe affected, but are expected to be
OL,21,Fextremely busy due to the disruption.
