OL,3,CUnion members from Aslef to continue
OL,4,Ctrain strikes over the weekend
OL,6,F"Having resolved disputes with all
OL,7,Fother rail unions, the Transport
OL,8,FSecretary and Rail Minister have
OL,9,Fensured that a pay offer is on the
OL,10,Ftable - taking train drivers' average
OL,11,Fsalaries from #60,000 up to #65,000."
OL,13,FThe union rejected an 8% offer last
OL,14,Fspring, with 96% of Aslef members
OL,15,Fvoting to take strike action last
OL,16,Fmonth.
OL,18,FThis would be the union's 14th one-day
OL,19,Fstrike since the dispute started in
OL,20,F2022.
